description: Inori has begun feeling a bit left out because she is too shy to dance with Love and Miki. She finds comfort in taking care of a little boy`s dog. When the dog becomes a Nakewameke, Inori gains the ability to transform into Cure Pine through the Kirun.

titles.title: Freshly-Harvested Fresh! Cure Pine Is Born!!
とれたてフレッシュ! キュアパイン誕生!!
